{"tid":1419010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒 唔標籤","createTime":"2019-08-05T22:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:23:11.000Z","uid":273319,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"43ac594dee9e24114493bfff4c7c52f9caf16d03","tid":1419010,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:56:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港嘅戰爭<br />\n冇勇武，冇和理非<br />\n只有香港人！</span><br />\n<br />\n長話短說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">標籤本身就係分化</span><br />\n群眾取態有連續性<br />\n將連續嘅屬性標籤並唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關於連續性：<br />\n<blockquote>舉個例<br />\nNumber 1至100, 50以上係大number<br />\n咁49.9係咪細number?<br />\n6係咪同40一樣咁細?</blockquote><br />\n用喺人身上更會將取態推向極端<br />\n推向極端後就容易出現割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換句話講<br />\n當前線手足不斷被吹奏為勇武<br />\n潛而默化就會覺得自己同參與遊行集會嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔屬於</span>同一個群體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家唔再講邊位勇武手足點點點<br />\n轉為比較客觀嘅描述<br />\ne.g <br />\n<blockquote>❎ 勇武巴打拯救北角<br />\n☑️ 今晚係北角嘅前線屌走黑社會</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>❎ 勇武派已迷失方向<br />\n☑️ 我唔係好明現場嘅決定</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>❎ 和理非不思進取<br />\n☑️ 希望只參與和平示威嘅群眾可以行多步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以謹言<br />\n防止被五毛分化<br />\n更加防止被同路人分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">係，呢篇嘢有針對「勇武」呢個標籤<br />\n因為對「勇武」嘅分化非常嚴重</span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c44d40946278e981cf156dd0236f7896fd714356","tid":1419010,"uid":63757,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:59:28.000Z","msg":"但左膠一定要標籤<br />\n<br />\n成事不足敗事有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c3b82e688ff5e84107d8c87866a4537518c5a6","tid":1419010,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ed0fa3ec18e3b673bbc9ef8c8115abbfba0598","tid":1419010,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2112327dc00febd397ebdec183f234dcc25a4ff0","tid":1419010,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:02:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7c10bcef2b89c94762fff81b7b51cdbb68df6c","tid":1419010,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:05:17.000Z","msg":"咪再指責和理非=無做野咁"},{"pid":"d87c9ce504ba2757628315322425a1a273292699","tid":1419010,"uid":209050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"[突發］話勇武＂戀權＂嘅人，請入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418897</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dda22dfa06e21c77cdd1f4886eecbbfb209f4ccf","tid":1419010,"uid":273319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c44d40946278e981cf156dd0236f7896fd714356","tid":1419010,"uid":63757,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:59:28.000Z","msg":"但左膠一定要標籤<br />\n<br />\n成事不足敗事有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:06:11.000Z","msg":"其實可以標籤件事<br />\n唔應該標籤個人<br />\n<br />\n舉例heidi新城市救黑警，件事好左膠<br />\n但你絕對唔會話heidi係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋一件事發生咗就唔會變<br />\n人呢，就會變"},{"pid":"fed0813fc10101b0940d66e8ccfaee02067c8282","tid":1419010,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7c10bcef2b89c94762fff81b7b51cdbb68df6c","tid":1419010,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:05:17.000Z","msg":"咪再指責和理非=無做野咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi